  "body": "## Feature Requests\nPaginated command line menu\nSupport for http imports for contracts \nSupport for a vendor directory for deps\nSupport for outputting dependency mapping into json format\nSupport for content addressable cache\nSecured upstream supply chain as much a possible\nA CI build that doesnt include libusb \nShasum and GPG signed releases\n\nAlso\ncorrectly init macOS bash_profile\nOutput JSON without the unnecessary non JSON comment \nBetter diagnostic TUI \nAnvil supporting OTEL/Zipkin tracing \nProtobuf support for defining fuzz targets  \nNon monolithic docker image \nNon alpine docker image \nSaving deployments like remix scenarios \nPossibility of replaying deployments from said scenarios \nProxy / upgrade support for OZ\n\nAnd\nReimplement solidity compiler in rust",
